Ok, the latest news JUST OFF The press!<br>
<br>
Zarathus HAS BEEN RETURNED!!!<br>
<br>
This means that there will be NO MORE TRAINS from any of the prior Evil Raiders members.<br>
<br>
I'm sorry for any trouble that I have caused but was very mad at SOE and since you're all part of the game I took it out on most of you.  If you post here a lie about me, you will not get an apology, but the posts that have been made here in this message thread have been mostly true and don't know how I can make it up, but you won't get any trouble from me in the game.<br>
<br>
I won't be fighting in the Bastion of Thunder for a while, but will be going to other zones.  Not for trouble though!  Just to build up my characters.  Yes, that's what I do, build of all of my characters so that I can fight bigger mobs.  I've never made any money from this game.  About the most I've done is bought characters and then sold them later when I found a better character to replace him with for a good price.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
By the way, just to clear up something, Truyth was never taken back illegally.<br>
